      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "MODIM anachnu lach, shaatah hu\nAdonai Eloheinu v'Elohei avoteinu v'imoteinu\nl'olam va-ed. Tzur chayeinu, magen yisheinu,\natah hu l'dor vador.\nNodeh l'cha un'sapeir t'hilatecha. Al chayeinu\nham'surim b'yadecha, v'al nishmoteinu\nhap'kudot lach, v'al nisecha sheb'chol yom\nimanu, v'al niflotecha v'tovotecha\nsheb'chol eit, erev vavoker v'tzohorayim.\nHatov ki lo chalu rachamecha, v'ham'racheim\nki lo tamu chasadecha, mei-olam kivinu lach.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:47:37.262Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "Eh7PdOyhknqixk3lOp4c"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3.jp2/376,368,1729,2004/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "5ce887a9-c30b-4ce7-9eab-bb0bc611a64d",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:438.70259638080233,2409.441384736428,3681.667977970102,1022.9740361919748"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "WE ACKNOWLEDGE with thanks that You are Adonai, our God and the God of our\nancestors forever. You are the Rock of our lives, and the Shield of our salvation in every\ngeneration. Let us thank You and praise You - for our lives which are in Your hand, for\nour souls which are in Your care, for Your miracles that we experience every day and for\nYour wondrous deeds and favors at every time of day: evening, morning and noon. O\nGood One, whose mercies never end, O Compassionate One, whose kindness never fails,\nwe forever put our hope in You.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:47:47.266Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "Eh7PdOyhknqixk3lOp4c"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3.jp2/438,2409,3681,1022/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "dd72426f-a5eb-48e9-933e-ec79f304c4d8",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
