          "value": "xywh=pixel:2323.6750590086544,3583.0055074744296,1817.4665617623928,1531.8646734854447"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "וְעַל כֻּלָּם יִתְבָּרַךְ וְיִתְרוֹמַם שִׁמְךָ,\nמַלְכֵּנוּ, תָּמִיד לְעוֹלָם וָעֶד.\nSHABBAT SHUVAH - וּכְתוֹב לְחַיִּים\nטוֹבִים כָּל בְּנֵי בְרִיתֶךָ.\nז\nוְכֹל הַחַיִּים יוֹדְוּךְ סֶלָה,\nוִיהַלְלוּ אֶת שִׁמְךְ בֶּאֱמֶת,\nהָאֵל יְשׁוּעָתֵנוּ וְעֶזְרָתֵנוּ סֶלָה.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ,\nז\nהַטוֹב שִׁמְךְ וּלְךָ נָאֶה לְהוֹדוֹת.",
          "language": "he"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:47:54.758Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "Eh7PdOyhknqixk3lOp4c"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3.jp2/2323,3583,1817,1531/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "61cbf140-360c-4f97-abc7-07775a5c9f33",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:423.124311565696,3588.1982690794657,1578.5995279307633,1412.4311565696298"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "V'al kulam yitbarach v'yitromam shimcha,\nMalkeinu, tamid l'olam va-ed.\nSHABBAT SHUVAH-Uch'tov l'chayim\ntovim kol b'nei v'ritecha.\nV'chol hachayim yoducha selah,\nviy'hal'lu et shimcha be-emet,\nHa-El y'shuateinu v'ezrateinu selah.\nBaruch atah, Adonai,\nhatov shimcha uľ'cha na-eh l'hodot.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-17T16:48:02.439Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "Eh7PdOyhknqixk3lOp4c"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3.jp2/423,3588,1578,1412/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "23be50cd-9bf3-4727-90c0-7ad972b95c8e",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:2230a76b-9265-4097-b1b2-0016fd2f36c3",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:407.5460267505902,5137.224053128709,3645.3186467348546,1047.3550184684582"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "For all these things, O Sovereign, let Your Name be forever praised and blessed.\nSHABBAT SHUVAH - Inscribe all the children of Your covenant for a good life.\nO God, our Redeemer and Helper, let all who live affirm You and praise Your Name in\ntruth. Blessed are You, Adonai, Your Name is Goodness, and You are worthy of thanksgiving.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, הַטוֹב שִׁמְךְ וּלְךָ נָאֶה לְהוֹדוֹת.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, hatov shimcha ul'cha na-eh l'hodot.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
